      <title>《读卖新闻》：丰田的错误认证也违反了联合国规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/toyota-s-faulty-certifications-also-breach-un-rules-yomiuri</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《读卖新闻》周二报道称，日本政府发现，丰田汽车公司多款车型存在的监管差异也违反了 62 个国家和地区采用的联合国标准。但报道未指明来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/toyota-s-faulty-certifications-also-breach-un-rules-yomiuri</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
