      <title>台积电相对于中芯国际的溢价表明中国芯片基金面临挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/tsmc-s-premium-over-smic-shows-challenges-for-china-s-chip-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾半导体制造公司和中国最大芯片制造商之间的股价差距接近近二十年来的最大水平，凸显出北京在打造国内芯片产业方面面临的困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/tsmc-s-premium-over-smic-shows-challenges-for-china-s-chip-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:44:02 GMT</pubDate>
